<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">在做连减的式子里，先将其互为补数或二数之和为整十、整百......的数，分别并加在一起，再从被减数中，依次减去各组之和即为其差。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">1000-636-164=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 1000-636-164</Run>
    </Paragraph>
     <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1000-(636+164)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1000-800</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=200</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>